Welcome to Color-ubble. This Privacy Policy is designed to help you understand how we collect, use, and safeguard your information. By accessing our game, you agree to the terms outlined in this policy.

2. Information We Collect

Non-Personal Information: We may collect non-personal information such as device type and device id, as it is necesaarry to save your progress in our game.

3. How We Use Your Information

We use the collected information for the following purposes:

We require a device id to be able to save your game related data, so that you have it the next time you access the app.

4. Information Sharing

We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties.

5. Security

We take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from unauthorized access or disclosure.

6. Your Choices

You can choose not to provide certain information, but it may limit your ability to use our services. Please contact us at the email below.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

